      <div id="about">
        <h2 id="about-heading">About Acta Prep</h2>
        <div id="about-wrapper">
        <img src="https://activerain.com/image_store/uploads/agents/dagnyeason/files/Andrew%20Dole%20pic.jpg" id="andrew-pic">
        <div id="andrew-bio">
          <p>A professional educator for over seven years, Andrew has served students from all over Fairfield and Westchester counties including New Canaan, Darien, Greenwich, Westport, Rowayton, Stamford, Norwalk, and Round Ridge, NY since 2011. Andrew earned his Bachelor's degree in Economics and Classical Studies from the College of the Holy Cross before completing his Master's degree in Classical Studies at Villanova University. For five years, Andrew taught Latin at New Canaan Country School where he assumed various other roles including Chair of the World Languages Department for three years.</p>
          <p>In 2016, Andrew started his own tutoring and academic support service offering an array of educational supports across a wide variety of disciplines. As a tutor and academic coach, Andrew strives to provide outstanding and effective support tailored to each student's personal needs.</p>
        </div>
